001package edu.cnm.deepdive.teamle.model;
002
003import com.google.gson.annotations.Expose;
004import com.google.gson.annotations.SerializedName;
005import java.util.Date;
006import java.util.List;
007import java.util.Set;
008
009public class Game {
010
011  @Expose(serialize = false, deserialize = true)
012  private final String id;
013
014  @Expose
015  private final String pool;
016
017  @Expose(serialize = false, deserialize = true)
018  private final List<Guess> guesses;
019
020  private final Team correctAnswer;
021
022  @Expose(serialize = false, deserialize = true)
023  @SerializedName("created")
024  private final Date start;
025
026  @Expose
027  private final List<League> leagues;
028
029  public Game(String id, String pool, List<Guess> guesses, Team correctAnswer, Date start, List<League> leagues) {
030    this.id = id;
031    this.pool = pool;
032    this.guesses = guesses;
033    this.correctAnswer = correctAnswer;
034    this.start = start;
035    this.leagues = leagues;
036  }
037
038  public String getId() {
039    return id;
040  }
041
042  public String getPool() {
043    return pool;
044  }
045
046  public List<Guess> getGuesses() {
047    return guesses;
048  }
049
050  public List<League> getLeagues() {
051    return leagues;
052  }
053
054  public Date getStart() {
055    return start;
056  }
057
058
059}
